Mecanic |  Skill                | ROG + BRD

Magic   |  Wuggan's spell line  | NEC + MAG + ENC

Curse   |  Rebbo's spell line   | NEC + DRU + SHM + MAG


<b><u>Step to follow | Spell(Magic or Curse)</u></b>

1- Sense a trap      |  <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=4257&source=Live" target="_blank">Appraisal</a> or <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=4263&source=Live" target="_blank">Augury</a> 

2- Kill the trap     |  <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=4269&source=Live" target="_blank">Discombobulatio</a> or <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=4275&source=Live" target="_blank">Exorcism</a>  | 1 x Greater Scrying Stone (17pp)

3- Open the lock     |  <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=4281&source=Live" target="_blank">Extrication</a> or <a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=4287&source=Live" target="_blank">Cleansing</a>

4- Then type /open

5- Loot the Object like a body
